_sText:
The object of this map is to break the floor. There is 5 levels of blocks and the 6th level is scattered. The 6th level is stronger than the normal blocks. Theres a way to get on top if you can figure it out. At the bottom is a pit. Above the pit you can stand on the crossing. There is also an Anti-Tker on the opposite side of SHOOT.  Have fun!
---
I recommend 24 people in all. Thats the Maximum players anyway.
---
Known Bugs
I don't know of any bugs. If you find one just post it here and I'll try to fix it.
